### ============================================================
### PASO 1 — LOGIN (ejecutar primero y copiar el auth_token)
### ============================================================

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@distribuidora.cr",
  "password": "Admin1234!"
}

### ============================================================
### CO-01 — Consulta de órdenes de compra
### ============================================================

### [CO-01-A] Listar todas las órdenes del tenant
### Esperado: 200 OK con array de órdenes
GET http://localhost:3000/purchase
Cookie:auth_token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJlbWFpbCI6ImFkbWluQGRpc3RyaWJ1aWRvcmEuY3IiLCJ0ZW5hbnRfaWQiOiJhMDAwMDAwMS0wMDAwLTAwMDAtMDAwMC0wMDAwMDAwMDAwMDEiLCJyb2xlX2lkIjoxLCJpYXQiOjE3NzM0MTI5NDIsImV4cCI6MTc3MzQ5OTM0Mn0.MCIqv8VnwVGDkybLj2pKLPcRrLM2o5-ed3C0TOSEUTY; Max-Age=86400; Path=/; Expires=Sat, 14 Mar 2026 14:42:22 GMT; HttpOnly; Secure

### Esperado: 200 OK con detalle de la orden (items, invoices, payments)
GET http://localhost:3000/purchase/{{orden_id}}
Cookie: auth_token={{token}}

###

### [CO-01-C] Sin token — debe rechazar
### Esperado: 401 Unauthorized
GET http://localhost:3000/purchase

###

### ============================================================
### CO-02 — Registro y verificación de pago
### ============================================================

### [CO-02-A] Registrar pago válido
### Esperado: 201 con payment_id y estado actualizado de la cuenta por pagar
### NOTA: primero debes tener un purchase_account_payable_id (se crea al marcar Delivered)
POST http://localhost:3000/purchase/payment
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: auth_token={{token}}

{
  "purchase_account_payable_id": "963b296f-03fc-4586-97a6-169123864b42",
  "amount_paid": 500.00,
  "payment_method_id": 1,
  "payment_reference": "REF-001"
}

###

### [CO-02-B] Pago sin campos requeridos
### Esperado: 400 Bad Request
POST http://localhost:3000/purchase/payment
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: auth_token={{token}}

{
  "amount_paid": 500.00
}

###

### [CO-02-C] Pago con amount_paid = 0 (inválido)
### Esperado: 400 Bad Request
POST http://localhost:3000/purchase/payment
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: auth_token={{token}}

{
  "purchase_account_payable_id": "{{payable_id}}",
  "amount_paid": 0,
  "payment_method_id": 1
}

###

### ============================================================
### CO-03 — Transición de estado de orden
### ============================================================

### [CO-03-A] Pending (1) → Shipped (2) — transición válida
### Esperado: 200 OK con nuevo estado
PATCH http://localhost:3000/purchase/{{orden_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: auth_token={{token}}

{
  "status_id": 2
}

###

### [CO-03-B] Shipped (2) → Delivered (3) — activa trigger de goods_receipt
### Esperado: 200 OK con nuevo estado
PATCH http://localhost:3000/purchase/{{orden_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: auth_token={{token}}

{
  "status_id": 3
}

###

### [CO-03-C] Pending (1) → Delivered (3) — transición inválida
### Esperado: 400 Bad Request "Transicion invalida: 1 -> 3"
PATCH http://localhost:3000/purchase/{{orden_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: auth_token={{token}}

{
  "status_id": 3
}

###

### [CO-03-D] UUID de orden que no pertenece al tenant
### Esperado: 404 Not Found
PATCH http://localhost:3000/purchase/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/status
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: auth_token={{token}}

{
  "status_id": 2
}

###

### ============================================================
### CO-04 — Consulta de three-way matching
### ============================================================

### [CO-04-A] Orden que ya fue marcada Delivered (debe tener matching)
### Esperado: 200 OK con amounts_matched, quantities_matched, is_matched y comparaciones
GET http://localhost:3000/purchase/{{orden_id}}/matching
Cookie: auth_token={{token}}

###

### [CO-04-B] Orden que aún no fue entregada (sin matching)
### Esperado: 200 OK con matching_found: false
GET http://localhost:3000/purchase/{{orden_id}}/matching
Cookie: auth_token={{token}}

